{"word":"οὐδέ 3","slug":"οὐδέ 3","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n75775\" key=\"ou)de/3\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">οὐδέ πω,</orth> Conj. and <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos> <sense id=\"n75775.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">and not yet, not as yet</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg003.perseus-grc1:322\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pr.\">Pr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">322</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg011.perseus-grc1:172c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Smp.\">Smp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">172c</biblScope></bibl>, etc.: in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, mostly with a word between, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδέ τί πω, οὐδ᾽ ἄν πω</foreign>, etc., always of the past (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὔπω</foreign>): later with <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg004.perseus-grc1:106b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phd.\">Phd.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">106b</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σὺ δὲ οὐδέπω ὁρᾷς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg033:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Merc.Cond.\">Merc.Cond.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: with <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ fut.\">fut.</a></tns>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὅσον οὐδέπω συμβήσεσθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2687.tlg001:2:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Zos.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.1</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδέποτε</foreign>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}